        <!-- SECTION 3: Computer Science -->
        <div id="section-3" class="mission-section section-hidden">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">💻 Prompts for Computer Science</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
                        <p>AI can be your coding tutor, helping you learn programming concepts, debug code, understand
                            algorithms, and build projects.</p>

                        <div class="bg-green-900/20 border border-green-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-300 mb-4">✅ Effective CS Prompts</h4>
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">1. Learn Programming Concepts</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Explain how for loops work in Python with 2 simple
                                                examples. I'm a beginner."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"What are loops?"</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">2. Debug Your Code</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"I'm getting an 'IndexError' in this Python code. Can you
                                                identify the bug and explain how to fix it? [paste code]"</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"My code doesn't work."</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">3. Get Project Ideas & Guidance</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Suggest a beginner JavaScript project that uses arrays
                                                and functions. Provide an outline of the steps to build it."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Give me a project idea."</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">4. Understand Algorithms</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Explain the bubble sort algorithm in simple terms. Show
                                                how it works with the array [5, 2, 8, 1]."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Explain bubble sort."</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
