                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                            <p class="font-semibold">💡 Pro Tips for Computer Science:</p>
                            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Include the programming language in your prompt</li>
                                <li>• When asking about code, paste the relevant code snippet</li>
                                <li>• Ask for comments in code to understand each line</li>
                                <li>• Request multiple solutions to compare different approaches</li>
                                <li>• Ask AI to create practice coding challenges for you</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Interactive Activity: Prompt Analyzer -->
                        <div
                            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900/30 to-blue-900/30 border-2 border-green-500/50 rounded-lg p-6 mt-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-300 mb-4">🎮 Interactive: CS Prompt Analyzer!</h4>
                            <p class="mb-4">Write a coding prompt and get instant feedback on how to improve it:</p>

                            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Type your coding prompt here:</label>
                                <textarea id="cs-prompt-input" rows="4" placeholder="Example: Help me with Python loops"
                                    class="w-full p-3 rounded bg-slate-700 border border-green-500/30 text-white"></textarea>

                                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4">
