        <!-- SECTION 4: History -->
        <div id="section-4" class="mission-section section-hidden">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">📜 Prompts for History</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
                        <p>Use AI to explore historical events, understand cause and effect, analyze primary sources,
                            and make connections across time periods.</p>

                        <div class="bg-green-900/20 border border-green-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-300 mb-4">✅ Effective History Prompts</h4>
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">1. Understand Cause and Effect</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Explain the main causes of World War I in simple terms.
                                                Include at least 3 causes and how they led to the war."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Why did WWI happen?"</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">2. Compare Historical Events</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Compare and contrast the American Revolution and the
                                                French Revolution. Create a table showing their similarities and
                                                differences."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Tell me about revolutions."</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">3. Analyze Primary Sources</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Analyze Martin Luther King Jr.'s 'I Have a Dream'
                                                speech. What were the main themes and rhetorical devices used?"</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"What did MLK say?"</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">4. Create Study Timelines</p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                        <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-green-300 mb-1">✅ Good:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"Create a timeline of key events during the Civil Rights
                                                Movement from 1954-1968. Include dates and brief descriptions."</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bg-red-900/30 p-3 rounded">
                                            <p class="text-xs text-red-300 mb-1">❌ Bad:</p>
                                            <p class="text-sm">"List Civil Rights events."</p>
