                            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Ask for multiple perspectives on historical events</li>
                                <li>• Request connections between historical events and modern issues</li>
                                <li>• Ask AI to create essay outlines or thesis statements</li>
                                <li>• Use AI to generate practice DBQs (Document-Based Questions)</li>
                                <li>• Request historical context for better understanding</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Interactive Activity: Prompt Template Builder -->
                        <div
                            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900/30 to-blue-900/30 border-2 border-green-500/50 rounded-lg p-6 mt-6">
