                            </h4>
                            <p class="mb-4">Choose your prompt type and fill in the details to create an effective
                                history prompt:</p>

                            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg space-y-4">
                                <!-- Prompt Type Selection -->
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold mb-2">1. Select prompt type:</label>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                                        <button onclick="selectHistoryType('cause')" id="hist-cause-btn"
                                            class="history-type-btn p-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-purple-600 rounded-lg border border-slate-600 transition-colors">
                                            🔍 Cause & Effect
                                        </button>
                                        <button onclick="selectHistoryType('compare')" id="hist-compare-btn"
