                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="border border-purple-500/30 p-4"><strong>💻 Computer Science</strong>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="border border-purple-500/30 p-4 text-sm">"Explain how for loops work
                                            in Python with 2 simple examples. I'm a beginner."</td>
                                    </tr>
