                                        <td class="border border-purple-500/30 p-4"><strong>📜 History</strong></td>
                                        <td class="border border-purple-500/30 p-4 text-sm">"Explain the main causes of
                                            World War I in simple terms. Include at least 3 causes."</td>
                                    </tr>
